desData.heading: City Description
desData.p1: Alder Manor is one of the best nieghborhoods in San Carlos. It has tree lined streets and the trafficis never so fast. In a normal weekend day, you will see lots of kids playing around on their driveways and moms pushing strollers around. So, if you have a young family you will be hardpressed to find abetter neighborhood.
desData.p2: The school district is top notch. The parents are quite involved and many children walk to schools unsupervised. This tells you that the streets are quite safe and neighbors watch out for each other.The size of the downtown is about perfect. Chain stores are not allowed so you will have a very small town feel.
